Description: Flat topped rim sherd of East Greek grey ware pottery dinos; dark grey fabric with mica and limestone inclusions; dark grey slip on exterior.
Curator's comments: Sherd joins British Museum 1924,1201.49, which joins 1888,06.626 and Oxford AN1896-1908-G.122
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (GL.045)
